data.description: Secluded and peaceful 1600 sq ft home on 3.81 acres, yet only minutes from Gloucester Courthouse area, shopping and dining. Upon entering this home, built in 2015, you will find living room area that leads into dining area and kitchen with bar. Off the kitchen is the utility room with a door leading outside. One one side of the home there are 2 large bedrooms, and extra living room and full bath.  On the opposite end of the home is the primary bedroom with oversized walk in closet and full bath with dual vanity sinks.  Outside there is a large covered porch, oversized 2 car detached garage with power and plenty of room to entertain.
